{"tid":182235,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"領展判上判，食店開舖3個月「被執笠」","createTime":"2017-04-01T07:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T00:50:17.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e01a5181fbcc8849818db668eb06befa2cba3f21","tid":182235,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:29:16.000Z","msg":"領匯領展又出事！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鴨脷洲利東邨街市去年改裝成利東海鮮食街，去年11月重新開業，當時有7間食肆經營，由三判「皇昌有限公司」負責管理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日前皇昌突然通知食肆4月1日要收回舖位，周五更拉閘換鎖，有食店東主投資30多萬血本無歸，10萬元按金亦未收回，質疑涉詐騙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n皇昌的股東和董事是親共社團香港廣西桂林市同鄉聯誼會副會長香明孝。"},{"pid":"45ccc111f3bdc1364822c74c0f3acb130dbefd76","tid":182235,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170401/large/1491027663_1c89.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170401%2Flarge%2F1491027663_1c89.jpg&h=19fe918c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n皇昌大股東香明孝日前突然指利東海鮮食街「人流靜」要求租戶自行離場"},{"pid":"abd94c013909e93b14d90858a5846af7193ed5f4","tid":182235,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"利東邨街市原本由領展持有，<br />\n<br />\n領展將該街市承租給宏安集團，由旗下宏集策劃有限公司負責管理。<br />\n<br />\n去年街市裝修後騰出空間增設「利東海鮮食街」，並把該處三判給皇昌管理。"},{"pid":"69d40a771c5b559a4ff1d5d15136603f549cf9f1","tid":182235,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e53b7cdac5c7e5c0a221e39f1825c05354815c18","tid":182235,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:38:25.000Z","msg":"領展 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9801262da369a19883a8fe75b59709f66608d04b","tid":182235,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T09:14:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利東邨街市原本由領展持有，<br />\n<br />\n領展將該街市承租給宏安集團，由旗下宏集策劃有限公司負責管理。<br />\n<br />\n去年街市裝修後騰出空間增設「利東海鮮食街」，並把該處三判給皇昌管理。</blockquote><br />\n擺明領展唔想理街市， 估唔到宏安集團萬有街市做得咁成功 ，外判出去畀佢哋都搞成咁㗎"},{"pid":"f31bebb415f520337ccd77552f131fcffe1ce9a8","tid":182235,"uid":49247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:23:28.000Z","msg":"簽租約冇話幾多年？"},{"pid":"b7e439a1c0c6ca192392fcac2359aca5e8118860","tid":182235,"uid":36849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:33:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cca00c07517ab0706d04813e20917d6666d9ad16","tid":182235,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簽租約冇話幾多年？</blockquote><br />\n寫左都無用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家d租約實有條款話「大業主可以隨時終止，不問理由，唔使賠」"},{"pid":"174aabcb29ce6717cfca21c5d7a2f1706b43b30d","tid":182235,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:40:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb2bc0a01d4c6f141befc6da2e2eb46cb6909f57","tid":182235,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:43:33.000Z","msg":"領展好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcbbe07d2f3207bf754815204d1cc24b1b44051","tid":182235,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T00:50:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>簽租約冇話幾多年？</blockquote><br />\n寫左都無用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家d租約實有條款話「大業主可以隨時終止，不問理由，唔使賠」</blockquote><br />\n咁就真係大陸格條款引入香港，贏撚哂!"}]}